    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >               <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217130/extras/73e7a4bca40855dc4789ec30de5e8504.avif?t=1738587995\" width=491 height=107 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plot Twist 将带您沉浸在文学行业的世界中，在这里您可以从一个不知名的作家崛起，成为排行榜上的现象。它将经典的模拟经营元素与原创的迷你游戏相结合，帮助您应对每一个创意和管理上的“情节转折”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217130/extras/b8abb421c433ed3758148ee570c48811.avif?t=1738587995\" width=525 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217130/extras/b1e68703ba988be8e45f3a52486a024c.avif?t=1738587995\" width=623 height=260 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从小做起，但随着成功的增长，建立一个蓬勃发展的文学工作室。雇佣编辑、插画师和营销专家来帮助您达到新的高度。最终，您甚至可以成为一名出版商，决定发布哪些作品——包括您自己的作品和其他作者的手稿。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217130/extras/2405249d20feadd7f6d28216c07dcf59.avif?t=1738587995\" width=525 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217130/extras/edf4251c288d3d29529afef00743a3c0.avif?t=1738587995\" width=623 height=260 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敢于尝试各种类型——尝试扣人心弦的科幻、感人的浪漫故事，或神秘的惊悚小说。你还可以以多种格式（纸质书、电子书或有声书）创作书籍，扩大受众，打动不同读者群体的心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217130/extras/c69087b2ef96490f0c6865db074e42ac.avif?t=1738587995\" width=525 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217130/extras/2d8594043ab09c09c7976ce3173255f0.avif?t=1738587995\" width=623 height=260 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在写作时，您将进入独特的焦点屏幕模式，选择您作品中需要强调的方面——深入的角色、扣人心弦的剧情转折，或引人入胜的场景。做出正确的选择将为您的最终杰作开启新的可能性和令人兴奋的附加内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217130/extras/d51ab37c1ce39e648f54a23c088c76bb.avif?t=1738587995\" width=525 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择合适的出版商，或逐渐成为出版商。每次发布后，密切关注评论——来自评论家和粉丝的反馈将帮助您完善作品，并将好书转变为真正的文学杰作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217130/extras/a9efc4de77b9818523b5a16624b56d94.avif?t=1738587995\" width=525 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217130/extras/edf4251c288d3d29529afef00743a3c0.avif?t=1738587995\" width=623 height=260 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plot Twist 不仅能激发你的创造力，还提供了有趣的迷你游戏，让你在不断写作的过程中获得休息。除此之外，在写作和推广过程中，你将面临各种叙事挑战和意外事件，带来新的机会或障碍需要克服。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217130/extras/0e7f7d250a8cf58c66986da9ec24d56f.avif?t=1738587995\" width=525 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217130/extras/e99bb78ab4b4485e5d7e31c78b78564c.avif?t=1738587995\" width=623 height=260 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过不断写作和发布书籍，您将解锁新的能力——从引人入胜的情节结构到精湛的文笔和有影响力的营销策略。不断发展，保持领先于竞争对手，确保您在文学精英中的位置。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217130/extras/0a6b5055936dae17dff6b1faebaac63a.avif?t=1738587995\" width=525 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将才华横溢的人才引入您的工作室——编辑、插画师和营销专家——帮助提升您的作品。每个团队成员都有自己的优点和不足，正确的专家组合可以将任何手稿转化为真正的畅销书！</p>",
